title: Is this Arisley Henrikez, the woman George Floyd allegedly assaulted?
subtitle: The police interview that led to Floyd's death in Minneapolis in 2020 was based on reports of a $20 counterfeit bill.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Araceli Henrikez, a woman who is alleged to have been assaulted by George Floyd in a robbery, appears to be photographed.
